Relativity/Hindrance(Streaming of Relativity)
=============================================
Relativity is one of the hindrance pattern/track that emerge in FOE(flux of energy streaming in brain) when other similar/near about object/objects is/are with one in any ways(voice/body language/direct information/indirect information/eye contact/comment/joke/challenge/jealous/..so..on..any known/unknown ways).
Due to poor understanding one realize the hindrance in himself when get in touch with similar properties objects.For only balancing the hindrance internally the FOE goes for relativity pattern and this pattern let it move to more hindrance state.

At extreme level everyone/object have their own unique pattern/tack/frequency, but when one try to mix from others pattern it create hindrance for his own pattern since after mixing one get confused for his own pattern/tack.

Relativity always keep one away form one self, Either one enhance their ego(feel good to look some step upper) or one get for competition(feel bad to look some step down).

Relativity makes one either grow or diminish worldly life but it never helpful for inner journey.
it is an interest that can get very easily, one just have to throw their thought in relativity . it is the sate that makes engage one in worldly life.

***One not with self, One must with others***
